==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Eight and nine are not separated from ten.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: bā jiǔ bù lí shí

===Idiom===
'''[[八]][[九]][[不]][[离]][[十]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# almost

#: ''[[目前]][[已]][[有]][[人]][[猜]][[得]]“'''八九不離十'''”[[了]]！！ ''

